(92, 96, NULL, 'Charger with powerbank\r\nUser manual\r\nUSB-C to USB-C cable\r\nBattery holder for GoPro 8 x2\r\nBrand	Telesin\r\nName	Power Bank for GoPro 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6 / 6 Battery\r\nModel	GP-PB-001\r\nCapacity	10,000mAh\r\nUSB-C input / output	5V / 3A, 9V / 2.22A, 12V / 1.67A\r\nUSB-A output	5V / 3A, 9V / 2.22A, 12V / 1.67A\r\nBattery socket	4.35V / ≤ 900mA\r\nOperating temperature	Charging: from 0°C to 45°C;\r\nDischarging: from -10°C to 60°C;\r\nDimensions	128.4 x 62.2 x 37.7mm\r\nWeight	Approx. 253g', '<div><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Going on a trip? Take the Telesin GP-PB-001 powerbank charger with you and rest assured that your equipment won\'t run out of energy to operate! The device allows you to conveniently charge batteries designed for selected GoPro Hero cameras. It is also equipped with a USB-A and USB-C port, with which you can charge your tablet and phone, for example. The capacity of the powerbank is 10,000mAh.</span><br></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">The charger allows you to conveniently store and charge batteries for the GoPro Hero 12 / 11 / 10 / 9. It also comes with holders that will allow you to place batteries intended for the GoPro Hero 8 / 7 / 6 / 5. The product also offers 2 ports - USB-C and USB-A. So you can connect your tablet, phone or wireless headphones to it, for example. The powerbank allows you to charge up to 3 devices simultaneously!</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">This practical powerbank can accompany you almost anywhere. It weighs only about 253g and is compact enough to easily fit in your backpack or bag. Take it with you on a camping, biking, mountain or fishing trip - so you can be sure that your devices will not refuse to work when you least expect it! You can also take it on board a plane without any problems.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">The powerbank attracts attention with its minimalist, elegant design, which is sure to appeal to many users. It is also very durable and wear-resistant. It has also been equipped with a special cover that protects its ports from dust. The device is also protected against overcharging, overheating, short circuit and over-discharge.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">You don\'t have to wait too long for your devices to be charged. The GP-PB-001 supports PD 20W fast charging, so it can renew the energy of your selected equipment in no time. With Telesin you will save time! What\'s more, it only takes about 2.5 hours to charge the powerbank (if you use the 20W charger). Note: when you use both USB-A and USB-C ports at the same time, fast charging is not possible.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Forget about having to recharge the powerbank frequently. The capacity of the device is 10,000mAh, which means that with it you can, for example, charge one battery for GoPro 12 / 11 / 10 / 9 about 4 times, and two such batteries about 2 times. You will charge a battery designed for the GoPro Hero 8 / 7 / 6 / 5 about 6 times, and two such batteries about 3 times. The powerbank will also allow you to charge an iPhone 14 about 2 times.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(84, 84, 83); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\"><br></span></div>', '1 Year', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/yjdFumK3jZI', 1, 1, 1, 1, '2024-08-23 04:36:42', '2024-08-30 04:27:53'),
(93, 97, NULL, '【3-Channel Charger】 3-Channel mini USB battery charger for GoPro Hero 10 Hero 9 Black, can simultaneously charge up to 3 batteries, also designed as a storage box to store your batteries.\r\n【100% Compatible with Gopro Hero 11 10 9 Original Battery】Rapid charging speed and steady connection, ensure all hero batteries fully recharged within 2 hours. You could use the Mini USB Type-C charger cable (inside the package) or a USB type C cable for power supply of the go pro charger.\r\n【Safe Charging with Multi-Protection】Design with multi-protection such as over-current protection, over-voltage protection, over-charge protection, over-discharge protection, over temperature protection and over power protection, offering a safe and reliable charging situation for your Go Pro Camera and batteries.\r\n【Clear Charging Light Indicator 】The smart LED light indicator prevents the overcharge of the battery. Red light means it\'s in charging condition, Green light means the charging work is completed.\r\n【Compact Storage Carrying Case Design 】Designed to be compact, small in size and light in weight, this battery charger & storage carrying box is easy to carry around for your outings. Keeps dust and debris out of your batteries while in storage or transit, protects your batteries from scratches and damage.', '<div><div>The Telesin charger allows you to quickly charge up to 3 GoPro Hero 9 and 10 sports camera batteries simultaneously. The advanced security system protects them from damage. In turn, the light weight of 27.5 g and compact size make it also perfect for traveling. The device has been equipped with special LEDs that glow red while charging, and green when the battery is fully charged.</div></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(97, 97, 97); font-family: Montserrat; font-size: 15px;\">The charger supports 5V-2A fast charging. It is compatible with the original GoPro Hero 9 / 10 batteries and it only takes 40 minutes to fully charge one of them! When it finishes charging, it automatically stops working, which makes the charger energy-saving and environmentally friendly.</span><br></div><div><div>The complex security system ensures that you can use the product without worry. Among other things, the device is equipped with protection against overcharging, overloading, overvoltage and short circuit. Freely charge the batteries of your GoPro Hero camera – neither they nor the charger is in danger of damage!</div></div><div><div>The device is also incredibly handy, lightweight and compact, which makes transporting it not even a problem. The small weight and dimensions of only 51.7×59.6×20.4 mm allow you to conveniently pack the charger to your backpack, suitcase or handbag, so you can take it with you almost anywhere – outdoors or on vacation. Your sports camera’s batteries will always be ready to provide the energy to create original shots!</div></div><div><br></div>', '1 Year', NULL, 1, 1, 1, 1, '2024-08-23 04:45:27', '2024-08-30 04:27:08'),
