(142, 146, NULL, NULL, '<div><ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">ighly adjustable microphone boom enables horizontal and vertical positioning for optimal microphone placement</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Perfect Effect - Suspension boom arm hold your HyperX Mic in any position you want. No sag, just rock solid. Mic stands compatible with boom arm.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Easy to Adjustment and Position - Rotates 360 degrees and a two axis swivel mount for giving you a perfect range of motion.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Mic Stand - Dual suspension springs of each boom arm protect microphone from shaking, suddenly dropping. It\'s sturdy steel construction, easy to setup and Folding.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">Mic Clip Holder - A standard microphone clip to mount most standard-sized handheld microphone.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">The length of single scissor arm stand is 14 inches which could be rotate 360 degrees with a maximum reach of 28 inches horizontally and 27 inches vertically.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\">The sturdy microphone stand with better compatibility even without hanging any heavy weights could be balanced at any position within adjustable ra